Plywood production, imports, exports, and consumption, by softwoods and hardwoods, 1965-1999

Dataset containing statisics for plywood products(3/8-in. basis). All units are in Million Square ft. unless otherwise specified.

  • Prod.Tot Total Plywood Production
  • Prod.SW Softwood Plywood Production
  • Prod.HW Hardwood Plywood Production
  • Imports.Tot Total Plywood Imports
  • Imports.SW Softwood Plywood Imports
  • Imports.HW Hardwood Plywood Imports
  • Consump.Tot Total Plywood Consumption
  • Consump.SW Softwood Plywood Consumption
  • Consump.HW. Hardwood Plywood Consumption
  • PerCapConsump.Tot Total Per Capita Consumption, in Square ft.
  • PerCapConsump.SW Softwood Per Capita Consumption, in Square ft.
  • PerCapConsump.HW Hardwood Per Capita Consumption, in Square ft. 

howard37

Format

A data frame with 56 observations of 15 variables

Source

US Dept. of Commerce, Bureau of Census, American Plywood Association The Engineered Wood Association, US Dept. of Agriculture, Foreign Agriculture Service
